<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="75400000t" end="98600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="182200000t" end="221000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="254200000t" end="263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="269400000t" end="291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="292600000t" end="316200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="317000000t" end="345000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="345800000t" end="357400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="358200000t" end="387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="388200000t" end="413400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="414200000t" end="441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="441800000t" end="451800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="452600000t" end="500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="501000000t" end="547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="547800000t" end="594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="595400000t" end="628200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="629000000t" end="652600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="653400000t" end="675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="675800000t" end="698600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="699400000t" end="722200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="750200000t" end="796600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="797400000t" end="817800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="844200000t" end="865800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1031400000t" end="1044600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">我一直在想</p>
<p begin="1051400000t" end="1071800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">應該為諾曼做甚麼才對</p>
<p begin="1084200000t" end="1113800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">答案是…甚麼都不做</p>
<p begin="1133800000t" end="1159800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">媽媽對我說過，她叫我放棄</p>
<p begin="1160600000t" end="1179000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">說之後會輕鬆很多</p>
<p begin="1179800000t" end="1211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">但是我又怎麼可能會放棄</p>
<p begin="1217800000t" end="1239800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">我不會令諾曼死得毫無價值</p>
<p begin="1245800000t" end="1254600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">阿雷，你呢</p>
<p begin="1281800000t" end="1305800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">其實我跟你的想法也是一樣</p>
<p begin="1311400000t" end="1322600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">不如逃走吧，阿雷</p>
<p begin="1328200000t" end="1341400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">我來就是說這件事</p>
<p begin="1349000000t" end="1361400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">我也想跟你談談</p>
<p begin="1371000000t" end="1399400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">這兩個月來因為媽媽在監視</p>
<p begin="1400200000t" end="1415400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">沒辦法好好跟你談</p>
<p begin="1431400000t" end="1457400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">其實我也不想讓媽媽察覺到</p>
<p begin="1458200000t" end="1470600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我真正的目的</p>
<p begin="1471400000t" end="1484600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">真正的目的？</p>
<p begin="1485400000t" end="1509000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">對，媽媽非常謹慎</p>
<p begin="1516200000t" end="1544600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我跟你明明已經甚麼都沒做</p>
<p begin="1545400000t" end="1561800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">她還是不停監視我們</p>
<p begin="1570200000t" end="1587000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">我們反而可以利用這點</p>
<p begin="1592600000t" end="1610600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">只要令媽媽集中注意我</p>
<p begin="1611400000t" end="1636600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">就可以令她忽視我以外的人和事</p>
<p begin="1649400000t" end="1659800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">阿唐和吉爾妲？</p>
<p begin="1667400000t" end="1690200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">沒錯，我交了工作給他們</p>
<p begin="1691000000t" end="1719800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">包括逃走的訓練和各項準備工作</p>
<p begin="1720600000t" end="1731400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">進行到甚麼地步</p>
<p begin="1734600000t" end="1748600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">已經全部完成</p>
<p begin="1749400000t" end="1777400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">工具和糧食、禦寒用品都齊備</p>
<p begin="1778200000t" end="1795400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">隨時都可以逃走</p>
<p begin="1796200000t" end="1806600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">做得非常好</p>
<p begin="1815800000t" end="1831800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">接著就是逃走的方法</p>
<p begin="1834600000t" end="1856200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我也想好了，我有一個主意</p>
<p begin="1862200000t" end="1878200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">在你出欄之前</p>
<p begin="1881800000t" end="1896200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">明天中午就逃走</p>
<p begin="1897000000t" end="1921800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">等等，中午逃走太魯莽</p>
<p begin="1922600000t" end="1933800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">情況跟以前不同</p>
<p begin="1941400000t" end="1960600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">逃走要選容易藏身的晚上</p>
<p begin="1966600000t" end="1987800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">聽我說，先坐下</p>
<p begin="2026600000t" end="2050600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">聽著，總共有兩個問題</p>
<p begin="2057800000t" end="2074200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">首先是媽媽的監視</p>
<p begin="2075000000t" end="2087800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">她監視我們的時候</p>
<p begin="2088600000t" end="2100600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">會照顧其他小朋友</p>
<p begin="2101400000t" end="2113800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">中午就更不用說</p>
<p begin="2123000000t" end="2135000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">至於晚上</p>
<p begin="2135800000t" end="2156600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">媽媽會跟小朋友在同一房間</p>
<p begin="2165400000t" end="2179800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">想全部人一起逃走</p>
<p begin="2180600000t" end="2197800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">就要避開媽媽的監視</p>
<p begin="2198600000t" end="2221400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">一定要將她跟小朋友分開才行</p>
<p begin="2236200000t" end="2258600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">接著就是圍牆外的懸崖</p>
<p begin="2263800000t" end="2279000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">不可以從那裡下去地面</p>
<p begin="2284200000t" end="2302600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">如果要逃走，就要過橋</p>
<p begin="2303400000t" end="2313400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">但是只有一道橋</p>
<p begin="2326600000t" end="2341400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">我想那裡一定有人看守</p>
<p begin="2348200000t" end="2364200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">如果逃走引起騷動</p>
<p begin="2365000000t" end="2379000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">警備人員肯定會過來</p>
<p begin="2390600000t" end="2405000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">而且那裡又很近總部</p>
<p begin="2411800000t" end="2432600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">怪物的數量應該多得數不清</p>
<p begin="2446600000t" end="2464600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">那麼怎樣？怎樣做？艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2505800000t" end="2527400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我認為用這個是最好的方法</p>
<p begin="2583390000t" end="2590190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">油？</p>
<p begin="2596200000t" end="2615400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">晚上我會在孤兒院放火</p>
<p begin="2624200000t" end="2645400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">即是說你要引起火災？　　沒錯</p>
<p begin="2651400000t" end="2671800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">就在媽媽顧著撲火的時候</p>
<p begin="2677000000t" end="2688600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我們以避難形式</p>
<p begin="2689400000t" end="2703800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">帶全部人出去</p>
<p begin="2704600000t" end="2730600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">只要事先封住通往秘密房間的門</p>
<p begin="2731400000t" end="2746600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">媽媽就通知不了總部</p>
<p begin="2747400000t" end="2762600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">總部會認為是火災</p>
<p begin="2763400000t" end="2773400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">與逃走無關</p>
<p begin="2780200000t" end="2801800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">那麼警備人員就不會去橋那邊</p>
<p begin="2807000000t" end="2819400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我們就能過橋逃走</p>
<p begin="2833400000t" end="2862600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">另外我會在森林死角的岩石後面</p>
<p begin="2868600000t" end="2896600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">藏起10個燃燒彈　　燃燒彈？</p>
<p begin="2897400000t" end="2921800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">別小看我這六年來的準備</p>
<p begin="2928200000t" end="2943400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">接著在衝去橋的途中</p>
<p begin="2944200000t" end="2974600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">將燃燒彈拋往旁邊的養育場</p>
<p begin="2980600000t" end="3002200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">如果順利，旁邊也會起火</p>
<p begin="3003000000t" end="3013800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">分散他們的人手</p>
<p begin="3021400000t" end="3037400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">晚上不會有其他人在森林</p>
<p begin="3045400000t" end="3054200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">所以沒事的</p>
<p begin="3093000000t" end="3110600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">好了，不要等明天</p>
<p begin="3111400000t" end="3129000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">今晚我們就逃走</p>
<p begin="3183000000t" end="3198600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">你做得到嗎？艾瑪</p>
<p begin="3219800000t" end="3229000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">沒問題的</p>
<p begin="3243800000t" end="3265000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">這裡距離大家的睡房應該最遠</p>
<p begin="3270200000t" end="3287000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">可以在火勢蔓延前逃走</p>
<p begin="3294600000t" end="3323000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">分隊逃走，在玩捉迷藏時已訓練過</p>
<p begin="3332600000t" end="3361000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">難道你的腿還未…　　已經沒事了</p>
<p begin="3377000000t" end="3389800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那就這樣決定</p>
<p begin="3417400000t" end="3425000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">阿雷</p>
<p begin="3446200000t" end="3472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">不過艾瑪，說真的</p>
<p begin="3479400000t" end="3501400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我一直都反對帶全部人逃走</p>
<p begin="3526600000t" end="3549400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">特別是知道圍牆外面是懸崖之後</p>
<p begin="3558200000t" end="3585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">最多也是帶走阿唐和吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="3591800000t" end="3619000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">再說，其實也應該留下小朋友</p>
<p begin="3627800000t" end="3643400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">這樣做是為了他們</p>
<p begin="3644200000t" end="3655400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">亦是為了你</p>
<p begin="3689800000t" end="3698600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">不過還是算了</p>
<p begin="3705000000t" end="3720200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我說甚麼都阻止不了你</p>
<p begin="3727000000t" end="3755800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">總比你不願意逃走，要留在這裡好</p>
<p begin="3756600000t" end="3769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">所以我還是不囉嗦了</p>
<p begin="3793000000t" end="3804200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">你自己決定吧</p>
<p begin="3853000000t" end="3863400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">還站在這裡做甚麼</p>
<p begin="3869400000t" end="3887800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">去告訴阿唐和吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="3888600000t" end="3905400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">你說將燃燒彈…</p>
<p begin="3919800000t" end="3942600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">拋過去旁邊的養育場？</p>
<p begin="3949400000t" end="3981800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">對，由你或阿唐負責</p>
<p begin="4048600000t" end="4081800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">雖然這樣，但我還是有點擔心</p>
<p begin="4082600000t" end="4101400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">就算我們可以引起火災</p>
<p begin="4102200000t" end="4125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">如果媽媽放棄孤兒院怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="4135000000t" end="4159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">媽媽很可能會放棄撲火</p>
<p begin="4159800000t" end="4181400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">反而會緊盯著我們這些商品</p>
<p begin="4182200000t" end="4192200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">你也察覺到了？</p>
<p begin="4205000000t" end="4228600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">這個可能性的而且確相當高</p>
<p begin="4234600000t" end="4256200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">所以只是引起普通的火災是不夠的</p>
<p begin="4265400000t" end="4281800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我們要確實牽制著媽媽</p>
<p begin="4287400000t" end="4303800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">然後再製造逃走機會</p>
<p begin="4315800000t" end="4324600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">不用擔心</p>
<p begin="4349800000t" end="4358600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">這樣做就可以了</p>
<p begin="4430600000t" end="4441800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">(輕燃料)</p>
<p begin="4466200000t" end="4472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">阿雷</p>
<p begin="4533000000t" end="4548200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">這樣做肯定是最好的</p>
<p begin="4549000000t" end="4576200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">決定出欄的滿分商品竟然起火</p>
<p begin="4577000000t" end="4592200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">她一定不會不管</p>
<p begin="4611000000t" end="4626600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">我一直等著這天的來臨</p>
<p begin="4635400000t" end="4650600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">很久之前已經決定這樣做</p>
<p begin="4657400000t" end="4677800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">我在很多年前已經決定了</p>
<p begin="4686200000t" end="4701000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">來一個幼稚的報復</p>
<p begin="4717400000t" end="4738600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">艾瑪，我告訴你</p>
<p begin="4739400000t" end="4765800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">其實我根本不是那麼喜歡讀書</p>
<p begin="4773400000t" end="4787800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">但是我一直忍耐</p>
<p begin="4788600000t" end="4801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">努力提升自己</p>
<p begin="4808600000t" end="4834200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">將自己的價值提升到最高</p>
<p begin="4851800000t" end="4862200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">12年了</p>
<p begin="4869400000t" end="4891400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我是他們一直期待已久的美食</p>
<p begin="4902200000t" end="4917800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">今晚我就要自己消失</p>
<p begin="4923000000t" end="4946200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">在他們等了很久的收穫日之前</p>
<p begin="4947000000t" end="4963000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">別以為可以享用美食</p>
<p begin="4963800000t" end="4982200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">別以為可以吃到我</p>
<p begin="4983000000t" end="5009400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">食用？商品？我才不管</p>
<p begin="5010200000t" end="5035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">我是人類，看著吧</p>
<p begin="5043800000t" end="5053400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">阿雷</p>
<p begin="5059400000t" end="5080200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">我覺得這樣最適合</p>
<p begin="5090600000t" end="5100600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">這樣的下場就對了</p>
<p begin="5110600000t" end="5128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">因為我一直看著家人去送死</p>
<p begin="5141000000t" end="5154600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">用他們來做踏腳石</p>
<p begin="5168600000t" end="5183800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">他們全部都很乖</p>
<p begin="5199400000t" end="5215000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">每個都很親切、友善</p>
<p begin="5223800000t" end="5235800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">等等　　不要動</p>
<p begin="5249400000t" end="5257400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">艾瑪，聽著</p>
<p begin="5263800000t" end="5275400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">機會只得一次</p>
<p begin="5283800000t" end="5294200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">要小心點</p>
<p begin="5301000000t" end="5331800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">不要令我和諾曼的死變得毫無價值</p>
<p begin="5334600000t" end="5343800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">拜託你了</p>
<p begin="5388200000t" end="5394600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">送給你</p>
<p begin="5461400000t" end="5472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">是那時候的…</p>
<p begin="5731000000t" end="5742600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">我現在12歲了</p>
<p begin="5749800000t" end="5772200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">雖然我度過了想詛咒的人生</p>
<p begin="5773000000t" end="5795800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">但是跟你們一起，我覺得非常開心</p>
<p begin="5796600000t" end="5812200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">不要，千萬不要　　謝謝你</p>
<p begin="5833400000t" end="5849000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">再見了，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="6527800000t" end="6547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">(阿雷)</p>
<p begin="6554200000t" end="6587400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">祝你生日快樂，永別了</p>
<p begin="6588200000t" end="6596600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">阿雷</p>
<p begin="6704200000t" end="6725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">這是甚麼氣味</p>
<p begin="6795400000t" end="6833400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">阿雷…</p>
<p begin="6871400000t" end="6894600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">阿雷…</p>
<p begin="6904600000t" end="6912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">阿雷？</p>
<p begin="6935000000t" end="6957000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">艾瑪　　媽媽，快些救他</p>
<p begin="6957800000t" end="6985800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">阿雷…他在裡面</p>
<p begin="6999800000t" end="7025800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">發生火警，快些找人救火…</p>
<p begin="7085800000t" end="7103800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">難道阿雷自己…</p>
<p begin="7154600000t" end="7161800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">媽媽</p>
<p begin="7162600000t" end="7182200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">吉爾妲，帶大家出去</p>
<p begin="7183000000t" end="7200600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">我房間的小朋友也交給你了</p>
<p begin="7201400000t" end="7208600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">知道了</p>
<p begin="7209400000t" end="7246200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">救命…</p>
<p begin="7256600000t" end="7265000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">快些</p>
<p begin="7307000000t" end="7344200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">至少也要保住大腦才行</p>
<p begin="7345000000t" end="7355000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">艾瑪，你退後</p>
<p begin="7384200000t" end="7392200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">阿雷</p>
<p begin="7463000000t" end="7491000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">灑水裝置呢？為甚麼</p>
<p begin="7491800000t" end="7513800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">艾瑪，你還是快些走</p>
<p begin="7514600000t" end="7527800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">再這樣下去，你也會…</p>
<p begin="7561000000t" end="7568200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">艾瑪…</p>
<p begin="7661000000t" end="7667000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">艾瑪…</p>
<p begin="8073800000t" end="8107800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">這些小朋友穿著甚麼鞋子</p>
<p begin="8189400000t" end="8198200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">她來了</p>
<p begin="8202600000t" end="8213800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="8227400000t" end="8235000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="8279400000t" end="8297000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">不好意思，要你們等</p>
<p begin="8373400000t" end="8406200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">謝謝你，再見，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="8547000000t" end="8564600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我接得很好　　你…</p>
<p begin="8565400000t" end="8579000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">我是不會讓你出事的</p>
<p begin="8586200000t" end="8603800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">小朋友們亦不會</p>
<p begin="8604600000t" end="8613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">小朋友？</p>
<p begin="8665800000t" end="8690600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">艾瑪，這些東西是你們叫我拿來的</p>
<p begin="8691400000t" end="8713800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">還有，大家都已經準備好了</p>
<p begin="8714600000t" end="8739800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">謝謝你們，托馬、拉尼恩</p>
<p begin="8764200000t" end="8786200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">快些換上衣服和鞋子　　阿雷</p>
<p begin="8843000000t" end="8862600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">換好了吧？那麼接著就要…</p>
<p begin="8863400000t" end="8879800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">慢著，不過…</p>
<p begin="8886600000t" end="8909000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">艾瑪，我…</p>
<p begin="8937000000t" end="8962200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">你這麼想死？有想過我們的感受嗎</p>
<p begin="8963000000t" end="8981800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">沒有時間了，我們要逃走</p>
<p begin="8982600000t" end="9005400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">艾瑪，這邊做好了…</p>
<p begin="9065000000t" end="9085000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">這些是…　　是你的替身</p>
<p begin="9085800000t" end="9106200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">這樣可以做出相似的氣味</p>
<p begin="9120600000t" end="9132200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">那束頭髮</p>
<p begin="9133000000t" end="9145400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">是安娜給我們的</p>
<p begin="9155000000t" end="9167000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">接著是發訊器</p>
<p begin="9172600000t" end="9182600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我幫你弄走它</p>
<p begin="9183400000t" end="9199000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">坐下，露出耳朵來</p>
<p begin="9207000000t" end="9225400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">艾瑪，這樣即是…</p>
<p begin="9238600000t" end="9262200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">阿雷，你不一定要死在這裡</p>
<p begin="9263000000t" end="9284600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">我讓你看一些東西，你乖乖跟我來</p>
<p begin="9293000000t" end="9333800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">是諾曼給你的口信　　諾曼？</p>
<p begin="9341000000t" end="9353800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">親愛的艾瑪</p>
<p begin="9364600000t" end="9387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">現在我在這裡寫下今後的計劃</p>
<p begin="9399800000t" end="9421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">阿雷一心求死</p>
<p begin="9433400000t" end="9463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">一切都是為了保住我和艾瑪的性命</p>
<p begin="9478600000t" end="9489800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">他這麼說過</p>
<p begin="9490600000t" end="9509400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">他沒有將自己納入其中</p>
<p begin="9522200000t" end="9534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">他沒打算逃走</p>
<p begin="9535400000t" end="9558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">他一開始就打算死在孤兒院</p>
<p begin="9563400000t" end="9585800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">他想藉著自焚，引起火災</p>
<p begin="9586600000t" end="9607800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">牽制著媽媽，讓我們逃走</p>
<p begin="9618200000t" end="9632200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">這個就是阿雷的計劃</p>
<p begin="9644200000t" end="9660200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">我不會讓這種事發生</p>
<p begin="9669400000t" end="9678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">絕對不可以</p>
<p begin="9699000000t" end="9720600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">所以我就要在這裡寫下</p>
<p begin="9721400000t" end="9731000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">我想出的計劃</p>
<p begin="9800200000t" end="9822200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">計劃在兩個月後實行</p>
<p begin="9823000000t" end="9847000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">時間大概在阿雷生日前一晚</p>
<p begin="9858600000t" end="9886200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">利用阿雷安排的火災救回阿雷本人</p>
<p begin="9894600000t" end="9923000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">比媽媽早走一步，帶大家一起逃走</p>
<p begin="9940600000t" end="9961800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">沒問題的，還有時間</p>
<p begin="9976200000t" end="10002200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">而且我還得到意想不到的物品</p>
<p begin="10011800000t" end="10026200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">是克羅妮修女給我的</p>
<p begin="10138200000t" end="10151000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">交給你了，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="10167400000t" end="10223400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">請照顧阿雷和大家，拜託你了</p>
<p begin="10345790000t" end="10372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">好了，開始了，諾曼</p>
<p begin="10512600000t" end="10524600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">阿雷</p>
<p begin="10606600000t" end="10623400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">好了，大家一起逃走</p>
<p begin="10624200000t" end="10647400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">一直走去圍牆 　　好…</p>
<p begin="10681400000t" end="10688600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">諾曼</p>
<p begin="10833800000t" end="10854200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">阿唐，到底發生甚麼事</p>
<p begin="10859800000t" end="10872200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">他們全部都知道孤兒院的…</p>
<p begin="10877400000t" end="10907800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">真實情況和逃走計劃？　　對</p>
<p begin="10908600000t" end="10915000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">為甚麼</p>
<p begin="10921800000t" end="10944200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">因為艾瑪告訴了他們</p>
<p begin="10952200000t" end="10976600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我已經告訴了其他小朋友，諾曼</p>
<p begin="11002200000t" end="11015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">其實那群小朋友</p>
<p begin="11015800000t" end="11032200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">跟阿唐和吉爾妲一樣</p>
<p begin="11033000000t" end="11050600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">都不是我們想像般不成熟</p>
<p begin="11061400000t" end="11080200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">為了逃離怪物的魔掌</p>
<p begin="11081000000t" end="11099000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">事先讓他們知道危險性</p>
<p begin="11099800000t" end="11114200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">讓他們憑自己的意志</p>
<p begin="11115000000t" end="11127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">選擇逃走會比較好</p>
<p begin="11142200000t" end="11154600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">而且媽媽</p>
<p begin="11155400000t" end="11177800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">只是對年紀比較大的幾個人有戒心</p>
<p begin="11195800000t" end="11221000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">這樣做很冒險嗎　　是很冒險</p>
<p begin="11221800000t" end="11250200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">但這樣就可以趁著媽媽疏忽時逃走</p>
<p begin="11251000000t" end="11265400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">要全部人一起逃走</p>
<p begin="11266200000t" end="11281400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">就只得這個方法</p>
<p begin="11303800000t" end="11324200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">最初只告訴四個人</p>
<p begin="11330200000t" end="11367800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">想知道甚麼？來，儘管問我</p>
<p begin="11368600000t" end="11381400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">真的甚麼也可以問嗎</p>
<p begin="11387000000t" end="11403800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">是的，農場的事</p>
<p begin="11404600000t" end="11428200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">又或者總部的事都可以問</p>
<p begin="11429000000t" end="11473800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">奈特、安娜、拉尼恩、托馬</p>
<p begin="11480600000t" end="11505000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">當時我們叫他們聽修女說的話</p>
<p begin="11514200000t" end="11524600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">這麼久之前已經…</p>
<p begin="11532200000t" end="11569000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">其餘的人是這兩個月慢慢加入計劃</p>
<p begin="11576200000t" end="11595400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">媽媽應該完全沒察覺到</p>
<p begin="11605000000t" end="11622600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">艾瑪假裝放棄逃走</p>
<p begin="11629000000t" end="11654200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">但是實際上是對大家發出指示</p>
<p begin="11673000000t" end="11697400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">逃走的訓練和各項準備工作</p>
<p begin="11698200000t" end="11711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">進行到甚麼地步</p>
<p begin="11711800000t" end="11724600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">已經全部完成</p>
<p begin="11725400000t" end="11755400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">工具和糧食、禦寒用品都齊備了</p>
<p begin="11756200000t" end="11767800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">隨時都可以逃走</p>
<p begin="11837400000t" end="11845800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">你們…</p>
<p begin="11983400000t" end="11990600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">諾曼</p>
<p begin="12095800000t" end="12112200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">我現在跟奈特先上去</p>
<p begin="12113000000t" end="12131400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">然後再拉大家上去</p>
<p begin="12132200000t" end="12139800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">好吧</p>
<p begin="12145000000t" end="12167800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">大家好像訓練時那樣就可以了</p>
<p begin="12168600000t" end="12194600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">要全部成功，平安逃走　　好…</p>
<p begin="12220200000t" end="12227000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">奇怪</p>
<p begin="12353400000t" end="12409400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">燒著了，全部都燒著了，但是…</p>
<p begin="12535800000t" end="12551000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">他們仍然生存</p>
<p begin="12551800000t" end="12582600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">艾瑪、阿雷還生存，你們逃不掉的</p>
<p begin="12583400000t" end="12605000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">我可愛的小朋友</p>
<p begin="12636600000t" end="12659000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">全部人都在這裡嗎</p>
<p begin="12713000000t" end="12721000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">媽媽</p>
<p begin="12815400000t" end="12868200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">(顫抖的雙手)</p>
<p begin="12869000000t" end="12922200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">(又再抱起一條生命)</p>
<p begin="12923000000t" end="12975000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">(在越加沉重的步伐前方)</p>
<p begin="12975800000t" end="13031400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">(請給我希望吧)</p>
<p begin="13032200000t" end="13057400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">(幾可亂真的平靜)</p>
<p begin="13058200000t" end="13080200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">(幾可亂真的平靜)</p>
<p begin="13085400000t" end="13110200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">(幾可亂真的平靜)</p>
<p begin="13111000000t" end="13139000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">(不想再次失去)</p>
<p begin="13139800000t" end="13163800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">(幾可亂真的愛)</p>
<p begin="13164600000t" end="13191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">(幾可亂真的愛)</p>
<p begin="13191800000t" end="13217000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">(幾可亂真的愛)</p>
<p begin="13217800000t" end="13244600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">(非前進不可)</p>
<p begin="13245400000t" end="13298200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">(定能越過障礙)</p>
<p begin="13299000000t" end="13338600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">(全因有你陪伴　給我溫暖)</p>
<p begin="13339400000t" end="13381400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">(無論多少次都會重新站起來)</p>
<p begin="13382200000t" end="13434600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">(想要一直守護你)</p>
<p begin="13435400000t" end="13481400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">(為小小的世界塗上新色彩)</p>
<p begin="13482200000t" end="13567800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">(照亮我選定的道路)</p>
<p begin="13568600000t" end="13613000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">(會感到恐懼　就一定沒問題)</p>
